            "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Warren Buffett And BofA CEO Brian Moynihan Speak At Georgetown University\" data-id=\"181192357\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3666px\" height=\"2444px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/181192357/image_181192357.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Drew Angerer</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>What's the worst thing that can happen? That's the most important question in investing and many other aspects of life. The second most important question is this: What, if anything, can you do about it? For at least two decades Warren Buffett has made it clear</p>",
